  "author_association": "NONE",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "According to the spec and parity, getTransactionReceipt should return a receipt for pending tx (in that case the blockNumber and blockHash won't be defined though)\r\n\r\ncurrently geth is returning null for pending tx \r\n\r\nThis is not as expected and remove a way to access details such as gas usage for pending tx :\r\n\r\nsee : https://github.com/ethcore/parity/issues/3569",
